creator: Marketing Mindz
descriptionHtml:
MINDZ CATALOG APP

B2B product catalog app for retailers, wholesalers, distributors and manufacturers.

Replace your heavy bulky paper catalogs with the Mindz catalog app. Impress your customers with high-quality product images, videos and full product descriptions which easily can be downloaded in iPhone, Androids and iPads.

Benefits Of Mindz Catalog App

Persona similar to BIG BRANDS
• Personalized Mobile application of the brand
• Complete information at the single place
• High quality user interface

Replacement to physical, pdf or ppt catalogs
• No more bulky, printed catalogues or paper quotes & orders
• Updates instantly - no more out-of-date catalogues
• Relief from too many handy documents

Display your products
• Get a sharp, visually-appealing, eye catchy e-catalogue
• Update and sync product changes instantly in just a single click
• Showcase product features using hi-resolution images
• Showcase high quality product videos
• Show full product specs and descriptions

Time and Money Saving App
• No need of any expert service
• No additional cost to update the product information
• Update the products without any technical knowledge
• Option to upload your printed brochures as well
• Easy-to-manage online catalog

Supporting Devices
• Works on iPhones and Android phones
• Works on iPad and iPad Mini

Ease Of Use
• Easy to use with Search and Filter functionality
• User Friendly Backend
• User can upload and change the product images, videos and description by own

Real Time Updates
• Timely updates with the new user interface
• Update on look and feel of the app
• Removal of old styles/pattern of the app
• Updation of new functionalities

Help Sales Representative to generate orders
• Sales representative don’t need to carry heavy bulky paper catalogs to display the products
• E-Catalog is helpful to attract the customer with eye catchy images.
• No need to deal with physical catalog
• Good for market presence
